data.description: MAJOR PRICE REDUCTION! Spacious & private home on 17.4 acres just out of town. With 5 bedrooms & 4 bathrooms, it offers ample space for a large family or for hosting guests. The two living spaces offer plenty of room for relaxation & entertainment, a cook's kitchen with JennAir cooktop & tons of cabinets. The large deck off the second floor is a great outdoor space for enjoying the scenery. One of the four upstairs bedrooms has an ensuite bath that makes life easier for guests or family members. The primary bedroom is downstairs with ensuite bath and large walk-in closet. Be sure to find the upstairs secret passage to the small loft that kids will love.  Outside, the 60x40 RV carport with concrete floor, separate electric and aerobic septic for your RV. Want to raise your own animals? Well water for watering the plants and animals, plus a barn featuring a dairy parlor with drain and a tack room plus room for two 12x12 stalls. This might be your next place to call home.
